34
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,590
Thank you.

35
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:35,830
You're welcome.

36
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,390
Thank you.

37
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:40,270
My pleasure.

38
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,390
Ms. Cai.

39
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,030
