40
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:48,190
Even if Jinhai and Li Group have issues,

41
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,310
that was from the last generation.

42
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,670
Here's how I see it.

43
