289
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,200
Cai Yanzhi,

290
00:18:21,760 --> 00:18:23,270
aren't you just twisting the facts?

291
00:18:23,840 --> 00:18:25,030
You were the one who shipped the goods.

292
00:18:25,040 --> 00:18:26,870
Your team opened the container.

293
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:28,270
If they weren't lost with you,

294
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:29,150
then where did they go?

295
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:31,030
I've already seen your delivery records.

296
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:33,990
It's all just worthless slag and rubble,

297
00:18:35,320 --> 00:18:36,710
so honestly, I'm curious,

298
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:38,950
who would pay seventy or eighty grand

299
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,190
