300
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:42,390
But what I'm even more curious about is

301
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:44,590
that Chen Zhuhe lost the shipment,

302
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,630
yet you're in such a hurry
to step up. Why?

303
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:56,550
Ms. Cai, to be honest,

304
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:59,750
I became sworn brothers
with Mr. Chen first.

305
00:19:00,720 --> 00:19:02,470
Your issue happened after that.

306
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:04,790
So, since my friend's in trouble,

307
00:19:04,800 --> 00:19:06,070
shouldn't I step up?

308
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:10,630
If it's my share to pay,

309
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:12,030
I'll pay for it without question.

310
00:19:13,480 --> 00:19:14,870
If it's not on me,

311
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:19,150
I won't chip in a single cent.

312
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:30,080
Ms. Cai,

313
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:33,470
I asked to work with you at the dock,

314
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:35,630
but you turned me down.

315
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:39,070
This time, I hope you'll do me a favor,

316
00:19:40,080 --> 00:19:41,270
but again, you refused.

317
00:19:42,480 --> 00:19:43,550
I am Wei Jinghai,

318
00:19:44,480 --> 00:19:46,190
the CEO of Li Group.

319
00:19:47,840 --> 00:19:49,030
Maybe I'm not that important,

320
00:19:51,280 --> 00:19:52,510
but Ms. Cai,

321
00:19:52,520 --> 00:19:54,590
you rely on the NCC for work

322
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:57,710
at the mining district in Kalpunia.

323
00:20:01,120 --> 00:20:02,110
Everyone knows

324
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:05,390
that we have close ties with Jinhai.

325
00:20:07,280 --> 00:20:08,270
But you openly

326
00:20:08,280 --> 00:20:10,550
keep Zhao Xin's son by your side.

327
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:14,030
I'd like to ask
on behalf of President Li,

328
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:16,870
what exactly are you trying to do?

329
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:21,990
Ms. Cai means

330
00:20:22,480 --> 00:20:23,990
there's something off
about the missing goods.

331
00:20:24,280 --> 00:20:25,550
Let's wait until we get the facts.

332
00:20:27,040 --> 00:20:28,590
As for what we're hiding,

333
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:30,350
we just haven't had the chance
to explain.

334
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:43,990
Mr. Wei,

335
00:20:46,400 --> 00:20:48,230
I've been in Hang City for a while now.

336
00:20:49,880 --> 00:20:52,470
I've heard a bit
about the NCC's history with Jinhai,

337
00:20:52,480 --> 00:20:53,390
so I know the story.

338
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:55,790
I came here today,

339
00:20:56,360 --> 00:20:58,670
hoping to get help from the NCC

340
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:00,230
and take on Jinhai together.

341
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:05,390
You mean

342
00:21:06,760 --> 00:21:08,470
you want to

343
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:10,750
take on

344
00:21:10,760 --> 00:21:11,670
your own father.

345
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:16,190
Why should I trust you?

346
00:21:16,360 --> 00:21:17,590
Jinhai went into Kalpunia

347
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:18,830
and took my friend's mine.

348
00:21:20,600 --> 00:21:22,790
I want to get it back from Zhao Xin,

349
00:21:22,790 --> 00:21:23,790
