355
00:21:40,760 --> 00:21:42,430
and go against his own father.

356
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:44,030
What a loving family.

357
00:21:51,040 --> 00:21:52,310
By the way,

358
00:21:52,320 --> 00:21:54,230
I have nothing against Jinhai.

359
00:21:55,040 --> 00:21:57,270
You need to work with the NCC now.

360
00:21:58,080 --> 00:21:58,470
That's fine.

361
00:21:59,320 --> 00:22:00,230
What do you offer in return?

362
00:22:02,320 --> 00:22:03,190
I'm embarrassed to say.

363
00:22:04,680 --> 00:22:06,990
Right now, I don't have much to offer.

364
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:09,510
But Mr. Wei, you can name your terms.

365
00:22:09,520 --> 00:22:10,790
I'll see if I can make it happen.

366
00:22:22,480 --> 00:22:23,190
Ms. Cai,

367
00:22:25,120 --> 00:22:25,910
