368
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:27,990
But you can.

369
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:31,390
I remember, back then, for him,

370
00:22:31,840 --> 00:22:34,230
you gave away an entire jade market

371
00:22:34,840 --> 00:22:36,390
to Chen Hongxiong.

372
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:38,550
I can't settle for less than he got.

373
00:22:39,840 --> 00:22:40,630
Mr. Wei,

374
00:22:42,360 --> 00:22:43,430
