381
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:08,950
Zhao Jiadi,

382
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:11,790
you want to stand up for your friend.

383
00:23:14,640 --> 00:23:15,830
We all know

384
00:23:15,840 --> 00:23:18,430
