00:24:25,280 --> 00:24:26,150
Are you saying

402
00:24:27,840 --> 00:24:28,630
I'm not capable enough?

403
00:24:29,560 --> 00:24:30,830
That's not what I mean.

404
00:24:37,040 --> 00:24:38,350
I just want you to know

405
00:24:39,320 --> 00:24:40,590
we share the same goal.

406
00:24:41,120 --> 00:24:42,510
Even if we can't be friends,

407
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:44,350
there's no need to be enemies.

408
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:54,630
Mr. Wei,

409
00:24:56,360 --> 00:24:58,830
looks like we won't reach a deal today.

410
00:25:00,960 --> 00:25:03,310
Why don't we both think it over?

411
00:25:08,240 --> 00:25:09,070
I'll take my leave for now.

412
00:25:12,160 --> 00:25:12,950
Jiadi,

413
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:14,270
let's go.

414
00:25:23,320 --> 00:25:24,630
Wei Jinghai,

415
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:25,550
what does that mean?

416
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:30,390
Zhao Jiadi,

417
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:33,590
it's a small world, huh?

418
00:25:38,480 --> 00:25:39,550
Do we know each other?

419
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:41,190
That's putting it mildly.

420
00:25:41,760 --> 00:25:43,590
My buddy got detained

421
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,790
because of you.

422
00:25:48,840 --> 00:25:49,310
Mr. Jiao.

423
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:54,030
Things have to be settled today.

424
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:55,430
Or no one

425
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:58,390
is walking away from here.

426
00:25:59,240 --> 00:26:00,430
Who do you think you are?

427
00:26:22,520 --> 00:26:22,990
Mr. Jiao,

428
00:26:24,760 --> 00:26:25,430
if we actually fight,

429
00:26:25,440 --> 00:26:26,350
whoever wins,

430
00:26:26,840 --> 00:26:28,390
it won't just be these guys
going to prison.

431
00:26:28,920 --> 00:26:30,710
It's just a fight,

432
00:26:31,280 --> 00:26:32,590
and you called the cops?

433
00:26:33,840 --> 00:26:35,630
I'm honestly impressed.

434
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:37,590
Coward.

435
00:26:38,560 --> 00:26:38,990
Yeah,

436
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:40,870
I am a coward.

437
00:26:43,320 --> 00:26:44,110
Mr. Jiao,

438
00:26:51,520 --> 00:26:52,310
let it go.

439
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:53,870
Do me a favor.

440
00:27:07,040 --> 00:27:07,830
Zhao Jiadi.

441
00:27:09,440 --> 00:27:10,190
I'll remember you.

442
00:27:11,800 --> 00:27:13,790
Let's talk
when you have something to offer.

443
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:16,910
Thanks.

444
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:33,030
I'm heading back to the office.

445
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:34,990
Go to the hospital.

446
00:27:36,080 --> 00:27:37,030
I'm fine.

447
00:27:41,240 --> 00:27:42,830
You've met him now.

448
00:27:43,240 --> 00:27:44,390
What's your next move?

449
00:27:46,280 --> 00:27:47,790
Wei Jinghai is neither

450
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,190
of those two types I mentioned.

451
00:27:51,760 --> 00:27:52,350
After meeting today,

452
00:27:52,360 --> 00:27:53,390
I have two questions.

453
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:55,640
First,

454
00:27:55,640 --> 00:27:56,470
just like you said,

455
00:27:57,240 --> 00:27:58,670
why did the Chen family go so far

