00:27:58,680 --> 00:28:00,430
to bring over things
that aren't worth much?

457
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:02,550
When you were talking just now,

458
00:28:02,560 --> 00:28:04,390
Wei Jinghai kept watching your face.

459
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,550
It's like he was testing you.

460
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:08,550
Second, about Mr. Jiao,

461
00:28:09,280 --> 00:28:11,070
he clearly isn't running
a legit business.

462
00:28:12,400 --> 00:28:14,590
But Wei Jinghai seems
pretty close to him.

463
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:16,830
It's not clear what their relationship

464
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,430
really is.

465
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:21,590
There's definitely more going on here.

466
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:24,470
Ms. Cai.

467
00:28:25,320 --> 00:28:26,190
Can you do me a favor?

468
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:27,590
Go ahead.

469
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:29,830
Find out more about Mr. Jiao.

470
00:28:30,440 --> 00:28:32,070
