477
00:29:17,360 --> 00:29:19,550
Friends from all over have come.

478
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:22,550
Guests are arriving from everywhere.

479
00:29:23,120 --> 00:29:24,190
I know how things work.

480
00:29:29,880 --> 00:29:30,680
Young man,

481
00:29:31,800 --> 00:29:33,510
