484
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:37,990
It's not the place for you.

485
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:39,670
So, head out.

486
00:29:45,800 --> 00:29:46,830
Hey man,

487
00:29:47,320 --> 00:29:49,310
