491
00:29:58,040 --> 00:29:59,670
You really think

492
00:29:59,920 --> 00:30:01,310
I can't pay up?

493
00:30:15,080 --> 00:30:15,870
Alright then.

494
00:30:18,840 --> 00:30:21,470
Fan Longquan is looking for Zhao Jiadi.

495
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:24,590
