503
00:30:46,600 --> 00:30:47,910
Zhao Jiadi just isn't up to it.

504
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:52,670
So for us right now...

505
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:54,950
The most important thing

506
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:56,590
