507
00:30:58,000 --> 00:31:00,110
Sang Ke keeps pushing us.

508
00:31:00,440 --> 00:31:02,110
The gap just keeps getting bigger.

509
00:31:04,040 --> 00:31:05,990
Dragging this out won't help.

510
00:31:08,480 --> 00:31:10,750
But at this moment,
someone is making trouble.

511
00:31:14,320 --> 00:31:15,470
Should I

512
00:31:15,480 --> 00:31:18,030
take some cash from the casino first?

513
00:31:24,480 --> 00:31:25,470
Even if the casino funds

514
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:26,870
get laundered,

515
00:31:26,880 --> 00:31:28,110
